    <briefdescription>
<para>Triggered state class derived from base class <ref refid="class_fw_state" kindref="compound">FwState</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The triggered state class overrides the handler function of OtaStart and timer expired events. In this state firmware update has been triggered by OTA start event and waits for the JSON firmware info. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
